                    <div class="text-lg space-y-4">
                        <p>We work closely with our <b>Board</b> and drive our myriad <b>public company reporting and compliance obligations</b>, provide strategic support and tactical execution on our <b>M&A</b>, <b>venture</b>, and <b>corporate finance</b> transactions, <b>equity programs</b>, and <b>corporate governance</b>-related matters, lead our organizational <b>ESG</b> efforts, and run our <b>global entity compliance program</b>.</p>
                        
                        <p>Contact us early and often at the <a href="https://procoretech.atlassian.net/servicedesk/customer/portal/114" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-orange-600 hover:text-orange-800 font-semibold transition"><i class="fa fa-wrench mr-1"></i>LRC Service Desk</a> or <span class="text-orange-600 font-semibold"><i class="fa fa-slack mr-1"></i>Slack us directly</span> when you have questions about: <b>Board of Directors</b> (including committees), <b>Corporate Governance</b>, <b>Investor Relations</b>, <b>Equity</b>, <b>Securities</b>, <b>M&A</b>, <b>Public Company Reporting & Compliance</b>, <b>Real Estate and Facilities</b>, or <b>Entity Management</b>.</p>
                    </div>
                    <!-- Back to Top link restored -->
                    <a href="#home" class="back-to-top">Back to Top &uarr;</a>
                </div>
            </section>

